{"tid":2459111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府宣布即時暫停接種復必泰疫苗   涉事批號為210102   另一批號210104亦因預防措施暫時封存","createTime":"2021-03-24T03:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be7d925e91d194fdaa08a53d2bf0a96ce299c77c","tid":2459111,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/162906603_4388196194621736_2826699947517199417_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=973b4a&amp;_nc_ohc=jFbgcamve2MAX-z5eZn&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=2ee76f7b6830c6ff5793eed37e62fe03&amp;oe=60808F56\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F162906603_4388196194621736_2826699947517199417_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D973b4a%26_nc_ohc%3DjFbgcamve2MAX-z5eZn%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D2ee76f7b6830c6ff5793eed37e62fe03%26oe%3D60808F56&h=0a2fd885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【政府指由於藥瓶封蓋包裝瑕疵 即時暫停接種復必泰疫苗】<br />\n<br />\n政府宣布，今早收到復星實業（香港）有限公司書面通知，由於注意到與批號為210102的復必泰疫苗藥瓶封蓋有關的包裝瑕疵，BioNTech和復星醫藥已就有關包裝瑕疵問題的原因進行調查，為謹慎起見，現階段在調查期間須即時暫停接種。<br />\n<br />\n到目前為止，BioNTech 和復星醫藥未有發現任何理由認為產品安全存在風險，但為謹慎起見，調查期間須暫停接種批號為210102的疫苗產品，直至有關調查結束。至於本港另一批號為210104的疫苗產品，亦須進行封存，暫時不予接種。此乃預防性措施，旨在持續確保疫苗接種安全。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於香港引進的復必泰疫苗屬於上述批次，各社區疫苗接種中心即日起暫停接種復必泰疫苗，直至另行通知。今日起已預約接種復必泰疫苗的人士，無需前往接種中心接種。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署今日會與復星實業（香港）有限公司舉行緊急會議，進一步了解及跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/4388196191288403/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F4388196191288403%2F&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2EPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=66201d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/4388196191288403/</a>"},{"pid":"7b6a5373c6fd364a74aa5664f1ab772a6fe87d97","tid":2459111,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"藉口藉口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865f796d0ffeb60a6a39c348d6a02a8074961c43","tid":2459111,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:10.000Z","msg":"做唔掂又爭住做"},{"pid":"c00a030939d97e9a05a3c921e756a2b3cb4c4d62","tid":2459111,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"得返科興俾香港人打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d404e4d5f05e1b0c6818c4ea438cc1890183cf72","tid":2459111,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00a030939d97e9a05a3c921e756a2b3cb4c4d62","tid":2459111,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:17.000Z","msg":"得返科興俾香港人打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:14:48.000Z","msg":"做完溝針實驗就會開返, 不過只準打一針biontech<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}